        <h2>The Journey of Hamad bin Ahmad Algosaibi</h2>
        <div class="history-intro-dot"></div>
        <p>Born in Huraymila, Sheikh Hamad began his journey with limited resources but strong determination. He worked in pearl diving and agriculture, building the foundation of his work ethic and his deep connection to the people of the Eastern Province.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:1rem;">His vision extended far beyond trade — he sought to build institutions that would serve the Kingdom and its people for generations to come, becoming a cornerstone of the Eastern Province's commercial and industrial development.</p>
